data.description: Live the Florida lifestyle with gorgeous views of intersecting gulf access canals and basin in this Olde Florida style concrete block home with wrap around front porch. This home features a Large great room, wide open floor plan home with 3 bedrooms, den, 2 and a half bathrooms and large lanai for entertaining. It has a beautiful disappearing edge pool, walk around dock with boat lift complete with a tiki hut where you can relax and sip your favorite beverages while enjoying the spectacular Florida sunsets. It is centrally located with quick access to gulf beaches.  It is also conveniently located near the downtown Cape Coral entertainment district, which  features plenty of restaurants and shopping. There are several upgrades such as hurricane shutters, an impact slider, newer AC and  lush landscaping all included. The home did not sustain hurricane flooding or damage. The property is being sold turn key.
